  slug the-dalmia-dadri-cement-limited-acquisition-and-transfer-of-undertakings-act-1981
  handle (2477)
  collectionHandle 123456789/1362
  title `The Dalmia Dadri Cement Limited (Acquisition and Transfer of Undertakings) Act, 1981`
  actNumber (31)
  enactmentDate 1981-09-15
  sourceUrl `https://www.indiacode.nic.in/handle/123456789/2477`
  sources obj_root_law_sources
  sections obj_root_law_sections
  hindiTitle `डालमिया दादरी सीमेंट लिमिटेड (उपक्रमों काअर्जन और अन्तरण) अधिनियम, 1981`
  actYear (1981)
  ministry `Ministry of Heavy Industries and Public Enterprises`
  department `Department of Heavy Industry`
  longTitle `An Act to provide for the acquisition and transfer of the undertakings of the Dalmia Dadri Cement Limited with a view to securing the proper management of such undertakings so as to subserve the interest of the general public by ensuring the continued manufacture, production and distribution of cement which is essential to the needs of the economy of the country and matters connected therewith or incidental thereto.`
  enforcementDate 23-06-1981
  notification undefined
